des: KNEO Sports Network is a ministry of KNEO Radio in Neosho, Missouri. We are the home of Webb City Cardinal, Seneca Indian, and Neosho Wildcat High School sports in Southwest Missouri. Our goal is to cover football, baseball, softball, and basketball while sharing the good news of Jesus Christ. We also cover other select schools and colleges randomly in this same market on a random basis as well.
